msgSnippet: These are four characters present in the Wikipedia Chart    which
messageBody:
These are four characters present in the Wikipedia Chart  which I do not find in the Junior Script font. And apparently not in the King Script font either.

I also don't find Eat, Age and Ash in the Junior Script font.

What font, if any, contains them?
